Here‚Äôs a concise Perl script that converts all `.mp4` files in the current directory to `.mkv` format using `ffmpeg`:

```perl
#!/usr/bin/perl
use strict;
use warnings;

foreach my $file (<*.mp4>) {
    (my $output = $file) =~ s/\.mp4$/.mkv/;
    system("ffmpeg -i \"$file\" -c copy \"$output\"");
}
```

### Explanation:
